Frank, Appellant, v. Post, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York, City and County, General Term. May 13, 1890.) Appeal from city court, general term.

Argued before Larremore, G. J., and Bookstaver, J.

Herman H. Shook, for appellant. Nathaniel S. Smith, for respondent.

No opinion. Ordered that the order appealed from be affirmed, with costs.
